檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"004d610deb7e7ed0336e80ca4befc24cf3568275","tid":1539300,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cd40aece60f5737d857c0c2edc563c69d37a8f","tid":1539300,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"❌撤回~是分化勇、和的手段<br />\n<br />\n💔 6月9撤同9月4撤回分別係邊?<br />\n在用手足的血和生命換取:<br />\n<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲 (元朗、太子)<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n失去9位生命<br />\n被性逼害女手足<br />\n無數催淚彈放題<br />\n腦出血 6個<br />\n骨折 3X 個<br />\n未計 metoo 同無出聲手足<br />\n所以絕對唔會就咁算！<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1200人被捕，受傷，逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n還有整個黑警濫權及制度的不公。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n☠請大家緊記下面每一位係天國與我哋同行嘅戰友：😭<br />\n熊家俊先生 (25歲) - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生 (35歲) - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐 (21歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu (29歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐 (28歲) - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生 (32歲) - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生 (26歲) - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生 (25歲) - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生 (16歲) - 2/9/2019"},{"pid":"c8e35c24e70d9eaa45a6f4b027ef11c15e640d3e","tid":1539300,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2489dc10b639aefa00b9ec76ba109e9af284035","tid":1539300,"uid":218659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6573502f3893b096426679e7c2860fe1b033bad","tid":1539300,"uid":38189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"講真今次運動有關蛇、何淦途出手一早贏左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T